  "commitMessage": "Use `name` instead of `id` in `NetworkConfiguration`. (#1648)\n\n- Closes #1647.\n- `id` will become a system assigned (Docker-like) identifier\n  for the managed resource, and `configuration.name` is the\n  user-assigned name.",
